We recommended management to: 

a.	undertake a complete annual physical inventory of municipal PPE and immediately reconcile the balances of any affected accounts with the accounting records to permit fair presentation of PPE in the financial statements;

b.	update the property tags/stickers of the properties to coincide with the barcodes used in generating the RPCPPE;

c.	maintain Property Ledger Cards and Property Cards for proper verification and accounting of each PPE item; and

d.	use the prescribed RPCPPE in reporting the results of the annual physical count of PPE.

